#. module: account
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:account.field_account_reconcile_model__partner_mapping_line_ids
msgid ""
"The mapping uses regular expressions.\n"
"- To Match the text at the beginning of the line (in label or notes), simply fill in your text.\n"
"- To Match the text anywhere (in label or notes), put your text between .*\n"
"  e.g: .*N°48748 abc123.*"
msgstr ""
"ການຈັບຄູ່ນໍາໃຊ້ regular expressions.\n"
"- ເພື່ອຈັບຄູ່ຂໍ້ຄວາມຢູ່ຕົ້ນແຖວ (ໃນປ້າຍຊື່ ຫຼື ບັນທຶກ), ພຽງແຕ່ປ້ອນຂໍ້ຄວາມຂອງທ່ານ.\n"
"- ເພື່ອຈັບຄູ່ຂໍ້ຄວາມຢູ່ບ່ອນໃດກໍໄດ້ (ໃນປ້າຍຊື່ ຫຼື ບັນທຶກ), ໃຫ້ໃສ່ຂໍ້ຄວາມຂອງທ່ານລະຫວ່າງ .*\n"
"  ຕົວຢ່າງ: .*N°48748 abc123.*"

#. module: account
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/account/static/src/js/tours/account.js:0
